reviewText: I have a TON of respect for Kenny Chesney after watching this. If you have a child playing football, or know a coach that needs a little encouragement, THIS IS BY FAR THE FILM YOU WANT THEM TO SEE. My son is a Senior, and I wish I would have gotten this his freshman year. I will be the one watching it over and over, for years to come! YOU WILL NOT BE DISAPPOINTED
Awesome...if you truly love football, this is a must have!!
Amazing documentary, I recommend to anyone coaching or who has a child in football to watch this!!
